'''CVSO 30'''是一顆距離地球約1200光年的[[金牛T星|金牛T星]]，在天球上位於[[獵戶座|獵戶座]]<ref name=Space.com>{{cite journal|url=http://www.space.com/33160-alien-planet-photo-cvso-30c-vlt.html|title=Amazing Photo Shows Likely Alien Planet 1,200 Light-Years Away|journal=|access-date=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630193859/http://www.space.com/33160-alien-planet-photo-cvso-30c-vlt.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，該恆星周圍有兩顆[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]候選天體（CVSO 30b與c）。

==概要==
CVSO 30是第一個以[[系外行星偵測法|凌日法和直接攝影]]這兩種方式發現周圍有行星候選天體的恆星。CVSO 30b的軌道週期估算大約是10.76小時，而CVSO 30c則是27000年<ref name=schmidt>{{cite journal|doi=10.1051/0004-6361/201526326|arxiv=1605.05315|title=Direct Imaging discovery of a second planet around the transiting planet host star CVSO 30|journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics|year=2016|last1=Schmidt|first1=T. O. B.|last2=Neuhäuser|first2=R.|last3=Briceno|first3=C.|last4=Vogt|first4=N.|last5=Raetz|first5=St.|last6=Seifahrt|first6=A.|last7=Ginski|first7=C.|last8=Mugrauer|first8=M.|last9=Buder|first9=S.|last10=Adam|first10=C.|last11=Hauschildt|first11=P.|last12=Witte|first12=S.|last13=Helling|first13=Ch.|last14=Schmitt|first14=J. H. M. M.}}</ref>
<ref name=FullArticle>{{cite journal|url=http://www.eso.org/public/archives/releases/sciencepapers/potw1624/potw1624a.pdf|title=Direct Imaging discovery of a second planet candidate around the possibly transiting planet host CVSO 30|journal=|access-date=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705064159/http://www.eso.org/public/archives/releases/sciencepapers/potw1624/potw1624a.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
Direct imaging of CVSO 30 c的直接攝影則是由位於[[智利|智利]]的[[甚大望远镜|甚大望远镜]]、[[夏威夷島|夏威夷島]]的[[凱克天文台|凱克天文台]]與[[西班牙|西班牙]]的[[卡拉阿托天文台|卡拉阿托天文台]]以測光和高對比光譜觀測達成。這兩顆系外行星候選天體都是[[氣態巨行星|氣態巨行星]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msn.com/en-gb/money/technology/amazing-photo-shows-likely-alien-planet-1200-light-years-away/ar-AAhocxR?ocid=spartandhp|title=Amazing Photo Shows Likely Alien Planet 1,200 Light-Years Away|publisher=MSN|date=21 June 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811163050/http://www.msn.com/en-gb/money/technology/amazing-photo-shows-likely-alien-planet-1200-light-years-away/ar-AAhocxR?ocid=spartandhp|archivedate=2016年8月11日|accessdate=2016年7月4日}}</ref>。

